Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.58,0:01:55.55,Planetes - OP,,0,0,0,,{\be2\fad(0,200)}hakanai inochi moyashita ikusen no asa ni
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.58,0:01:55.55,Planetes - OP,,0,0,20,,{\an2\be2\fad(0,200)}It set their ephemeral souls on fire on a thousand mornings.
