Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.76,0:02:07.06,Planetes - OP,,0,0,20,,{\an2\be2\fad(0,200)}I bet they're taking right to where the light is headed.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.83,0:02:06.54,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,♪羽ばたくだろう
